   Renders a single ``_REPORT.md`` into the replica root. The
   summary extractor's output goes in verbatim; everything else
   gets a one-line per-kind tally with names listed inline.

   Inputs:
     basename       — source basename
     topic          — classify topic string
     quintet        — classify quintet object
     summary        — extract-summary's text (verbatim)
     extractions    — {kind: [items]}, items have ``name`` field
     synthesis_paths — list of ``21 SYNTHESIS/<slug>.md`` paths
                       written by the synthesis agent (may be
                       empty)
     manifest_modifications  — [{vault_path, kind, name}] for
                               artifact pages that overwrite an
                               existing vault page (manifest
                               entries with op=modified)
     synthesis_modifications — [{vault_path, name}] for synthesis
                               pages whose path already exists in
                               the vault and would be overwritten
